Each race win gives 25 points, 2nd place gives 18, 3rd place gives 15, 4th place gives 12, 5th place gives 10, 6th place gives 8, 7th place gives 6, 8th place gives 4, 9th place gives 2, and 10th place gives 1 point.
Race wins may be nullified by the FTA. If so, the win and points go to the next place.
Places may also be nullified by the FTA.
Championship wins may be voided if misconduct was found.
